powerpc/boot: Make use of REL16 relocs in powerpc/boot/util.S

Use bcl 20,31,0f rather than plain bl to avoid unbalancing the link
stack.

Update the code to use REL16 relocs, available for ppc64 in 2009 (and
ppc32 in 2005).

